
Node:	hot_not (Spoken declaration of whether or not something is hot)
Input:
	Speech keyword: "Temperature"
Config: 
	srv_temp > 30.0	"It is hot."
				o/w "It is not hot."
	string hot_color: "red"
	string cold_color: "blue"
Output:
	None
Steps:
	1. Initialization: Begin subscribing to tpc_speech (100Hz)
	2. if keyword is detected, then send request to srv_temp
	3. if temperature is greater than or equal to 30.0 then:
		(a) Send request to srv_speaker ("It is Hot")
		(b) Publish hot_color to tpc_colors
	4. else if temperature is less than 30.0 then:
		(a) Send request to srv_speaker ("It is not hot")
		(b) Publish cold_color to tpc_colors



Waiting on speech recognition package details
